    <string name="about1">Zazen Meditation Timer — A simple meditation timer with customizable sections, bell sounds, and session management.</string>
    <string name="about2">Originally created by Stefan Gaffga. Currently maintained by Georg Graf.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Thanks to Winfried of &lt;a href="http://www.meditationsuhren.de"&gt;http://www.meditationsuhren.de&lt;/a&gt; for providing such great Bell Sounds!</string>
    <string name="about3">&lt;a href="https://github.com/georgernstgraf/zazentimer/issues"&gt;Report issues on GitHub&lt;/a&gt;</string>
    <string name="app_description">This application lets the user define a set of meditation sessions and provides a timer with visual and audible feedback when a part or the whole meditation is over.</string>
